<title type="html"><![CDATA[Classic Shell 4.2.5 is released  [Nov 14th 2015]]]></title>

<content type="html" xml:base="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?t=5363&amp;p=23469#p23469"><![CDATA[
Classic Shell 4.2.5 was just released. Download it from here: <!-- m --><a class="postlink" href="http://www.mediafire.com/download/me939aalo1rrstm/ClassicShellSetup_4_2_5.exe">http://www.mediafire.com/download/me939 ... _4_2_5.exe</a><!-- m --><br /><br />Here’s what’s new:<ul><li> Improved support for Windows 10 TH2</li><li> Improved support for the Edge browser</li><li> Improved search performance and responsiveness</li><li> New feature to uninstall Metro apps from the start menu</li><li> Full transparency support for the Metro and Midnight skins</li></ul><br /><br />Next release is <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=6073" class="postlink">Classic Shell 4.2.6</a><br />Previous release was <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/viewtopic.php?f=4&amp;t=4938" class="postlink">Classic Shell 4.2.4</a><p>Statistics: Posted by <a href="http://www.classicshell.net/forum/memberlist.php?mode=viewprofile&amp;u=2">Ivo</a> — Sat Nov 14, 2015 11:24 am</p><hr />
]]></content>
